overview: The fellowship of the Knees is now separated. Freedo and Sammison are on their way to the red room along with the untrustworthy Golluum as PP Pippin and Merry Mary encounter the talking giant dildos. As Aragone, Leg Man Legolas and Pedo Dwarf Man defend the city of Rape Town while Saruwoman and Sauron With Pencil get closer the the one knee to rule them all.
